{"type":"article","id":10888,"title":"墙内同人小说网站刺猬猫近日遭遇赵弹，原因竟然是……","uid":14002,"topics":[86,158,2371,3188,17],"contents":"最近，墙内小说网站刺猬猫向作者发布如下公告：<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/24fa50a011e0cf978b89a.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/24fa50a011e0cf978b89a.png\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/24fa50a011e0cf978b89a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n发生了什么？刺猬猫为什么会被赵弹打击？<br>\n我也是这个站点的作者，但是对此事毫不知情。<br>\n后来我从刺猬猫讨论群里找到了一些蛛丝马迹：<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/595cc6d3ef41c8e21dda9.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/595cc6d3ef41c8e21dda9.jpg\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/595cc6d3ef41c8e21dda9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n原来是有人直球冲塔，恶政隐。<br>\n有些人表面上是舟游玩家，背后却是反贼。<br>\n群里随即进行了热烈（而且恶臭不堪）的讨论：<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ff30d79d23d4b9e74e0b8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ff30d79d23d4b9e74e0b8.jpg\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ff30d79d23d4b9e74e0b8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2f4e23c5ed2707851c99a.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2f4e23c5ed2707851c99a.jpg\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2f4e23c5ed2707851c99a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n现在这位同志的作品已经在刺猬猫和晋江被橄榄，但在墙内还有，而且居然还在更新。<br>\n真是冲塔中的豪杰！<br>\n链接：https://www.30sy.com/book/wodetalulabukenengnamekeai/<br>\nhttps://www.gzbpi.com/shu/2058998/<br>\nP.S. 该群小粉红确实很多……<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cd0c918e2d034acf169b3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cd0c918e2d034acf169b3.jpg\" alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cd0c918e2d034acf169b3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-14","agreeCount":11,"discussionCount":0}